BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:QkMQNtqLfQWZ-yv2jYIID
SUMMARY:Black Label Society
DTSTAMP:20260314T153647Z
DTSTART:20260317T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Paramount Theatre is located in downtown Seattle at 911 Pin
	e Street\, Seattle\, WA 98101. There is an overall 4 ticket limit per patr
	on. Patrons exceeding the ticket limit will have their orders canceled at 
	the venue's discretion. All sales are final. No refunds or exchanges. Mobi
	le barcodes delayed until 4 days prior to event. Venue reserves the right 
	to change delivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\, each person must have
	 a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. There is no elevator. Stai
	rs only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors & bag search at door. Arriv
	e early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety When purchasing ADA 
	accessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by email if assistance
	 is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; you may reach us at 
	accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses an armless free
	standing chair for patrons with mobility impairments and their companions.
	 Please note that our historic theatre has no elevator to the balcony leve
	ls. Please note\, the ADA section on the seating map does not represent a 
	specific seat location.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/black-label-societ
	y-seattle-washington-03-16-2026/event/0F006367F9A4A49A\n\nFrom STG - Param
	ount Theatre
URL:https://www.ticketmaster.com/black-label-society-seattle-washington-03-
	16-2026/event/0F006367F9A4A49A
LOCATION:Paramount Theatre\, 911 Pine St\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:stg-paramount
CATEGORIES:STG - Paramount Theatre
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
